### Create Savings Goal
POST {{baseUrl}}/savings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Emergency Fund",
  "targetAmount": 5000,
  "currentAmount": 800,
  "targetDate": "2026-12-31T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Get Savings Goals
GET {{baseUrl}}/savings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Savings Goal By Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/savings/{{savingsId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Savings Goal
PUT {{baseUrl}}/savings/{{savingsId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Emergency Fund Updated",
  "targetAmount": 6000,
  "currentAmount": 1200,
  "targetDate": "2026-12-31T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Delete Savings Goal
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/savings/{{savingsId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
